          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-397-ROGP-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-397-ROGP-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-397-ROGP-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-397-ROGP-line-1" n="1">Mordanto fills the trump of fame,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-397-ROGP-line-2" n="2">The Christian world his deeds proclaim,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-397-ROGP-line-3" n="3">And prints are crowded with his name.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-397-ROGP-line-4" n="4"><lb/>In journeys he outrides the post,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-397-ROGP-line-5" n="5">Sits up till midnight with his host,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-397-ROGP-line-6" n="6">Talks politics, and gives the toast.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-397-ROGP-line-7" n="7"><lb/>Knows every prince in Europe's face,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-397-ROGP-line-8" n="8">Flies like a squib from place to place,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-397-ROGP-line-9" n="9">And travels not, but runs a race.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-397-ROGP-line-10" n="10"><lb/>From Paris Gazette <hi rend="italics">Ã  la main</hi>,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-397-ROGP-line-11" n="11">This day arrived without his train,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-397-ROGP-line-12" n="12">Mordanto in a week from Spain.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-397-ROGP-line-13" n="13"><lb/>A messenger comes all a-reek,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-397-ROGP-line-14" n="14">Mordanto at Madrid to seek:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-397-ROGP-line-15" n="15">He left the town above a week.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-397-ROGP-line-16" n="16">Next day the post-boy winds his horn,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-397-ROGP-line-17" n="17">And rides through Dover in the morn:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-397-ROGP-line-18" n="18">Mordanto's landed from Leghorn.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-397-ROGP-line-19" n="19"><lb/>Mordanto gallops on alone,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-397-ROGP-line-20" n="20">The roads are with his followers strewn,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-397-ROGP-line-21" n="21">This breaks a girth, and that a bone.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-397-ROGP-line-22" n="22"><lb/>His body active as his mind,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-397-ROGP-line-23" n="23">Returning sound in limb and wind,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-397-ROGP-line-24" n="24">Except some leather lost behind.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-397-ROGP-line-25" n="25"><lb/>A skeleton in outward figure,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-397-ROGP-line-26" n="26">His meagre corpse, though full of vigour,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-397-ROGP-line-27" n="27">Would halt behind him, were it bigger.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-397-ROGP-line-28" n="28"><lb/>So wonderful his expedition,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-397-ROGP-line-29" n="29">When you have not the least suspicion,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-397-ROGP-line-30" n="30">He's with you like an apparition.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-397-ROGP-line-31" n="31"><lb/>Shines in all climates like a star;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-397-ROGP-line-32" n="32">In senates bold, and fierce in war,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-397-ROGP-line-33" n="33">A land commander, and a tar.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-397-ROGP-line-34" n="34"><lb/>Heroic actions early bred in,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-397-ROGP-line-35" n="35">Ne'er to be matched in modern reading,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-397-ROGP-line-36" n="36">But by his namesake Charles of Sweden.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
